# Linux notes

## What is Linux

 Linux is an operating system that is used to run servers and cloud platforms. it is stable, reliable,free and open source. 

## Why learn Linux

 * Most servers run Linux 
 * Linux is stable
 * Linux is secure
 * DevOps engineers use Linux daily 

## what I learnt today

 Linux is basically the backbone of internet servers, it runs in servers and cloud platforms for effective networking, it's free, reliable and saves cost for engineers who use it and it is stable.  